ustom ARM-based System-on-Chips...\r Read more...\r \r \r \r \r News\r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r by \r \r Joshua Gulick\r —\r Tuesday, March 31, 2015\r \r \r LG And Samsung End Spin Cycle, Call Off Silly Spat Over Sabotaged Washing Machines\r \r \r \r If you don’t think that competition between washing machine manufacturers is thrilling, you haven’t been paying attention to the bitter struggle between South Korean electronics companies LG and Samsung. The drama has included accusations of...\r Read more...\r \r \r \r \r News\r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r  1 2 3 4 5 Next ... Last\r \r \r \r \r \r Follow Us:\r \r   Twitter\r   Facebook\r   RSS\r   Email\r   YouTube\r   AppStore\r   Google+\r \r \r \r \r \r \r 55K\r 7K\r 4K\r \r 18K\r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r \r   \r    \r     CONVERSATIONS\r     \r      Oops! LG Accidentally Leaks...13\r      Middle Schooler Charged With Felony For...11\r      Time Warner Cable Counters Google Fiber...8\r      Google X Skunkworks Lab Is Cooking Up...7\r      How Private Is Your Cloud? Google Could...7\r      ESA Says Required ''Hacking'' Makes...6\r      US Government Rejects Intel’s Attempt...6\r     \r    \r \r    \r     FEATURED\r     \r      HTC One M9 Review: Lollipop, Octa-Core...\r      Sony Xperia Z3v Smartphone For Verizon...\r      Moto 360 Review: Android Wear-Powered...\r      CyberPower Syber Vapor PC Gaming Console...\r      Intel SSD 750 Series NVMe PCI Express...\r      Samsung SSD 850 EVO mSATA and M.2 Drives...\r      Gigabyte Brix S BXi7H-5500 Broadwell...\r     \r    \r \r    \r     FAVORITES\r     \r      Know Your Type: Five Mechanical Gaming...357k\r      6 TB Hard Drive Round-Up: WD Red, WD...341k\r      Dell XPS 13 (2015) Ultrabook,...334k\r      Intel SSD 750 Series NVMe PCI Express...229k\r      Alienware Area-51: Triad, Tri-SLI GTX...154k\r      Asus Zenbook UX305 Ultrabook Review:...150k\r      HP Spectre X360 Ultrabook Review: Sleek,...143k\r     \r    \r 